Class TempTableMgr

java.lang.Object
  kdl.prox.qgraph2.TempTableMgr

public class TempTableMgr
extends java.lang.Object

Helper class instantiated by QueryGraph2CompOp.execTGPath() and used by Transformation instances to manage the mapping of ConsQGVertex names to temporary SGI NSTs.
